HEADWORD: Helpful
<hw>Help"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Furnishing help;
giving aid; assistant; useful; salutary.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Heavens make our presence and our practices⟦br⟧
Pleasant and <qex>helpful</qex> to him!</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj></p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Help"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Help"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>helping</ent>⟦br⟧
